To launch couchdb please use https://docs.couchdb.org/en/latest/install/unix.html
Use instalation with sources. Mirrors: https://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.lua?path=/couchdb/source/2.3.1/apache-couchdb-2.3.1.tar.gz
To make things work on Windows - please copy openssl dll's to C:/Windows/SysWOW64
To make Client work on ubuntu - sudo apt install libgl1-mesa-dev
To run couchdb: sudo -i -u couchdb /home/couchdb/bin/couchdb
